734
01:19:30.040 --> 01:19:31.560 line:80%
It's him or you.

735
01:19:32.360 --> 01:19:33.560 line:80%
Four more minutes.

736
01:19:34.280 --> 01:19:35.280 line:80%
You have to kill him.

737
