809
01:27:04.040 --> 01:27:06.640 line:80%
Last year, we had...

810
01:27:07.720 --> 01:27:10.520 line:80%
Hello. My name is Martin.
I'm 44 and I beat my wife.

811
01:27:11.600 --> 01:27:14.640 line:80%
