823
01:27:38.120 --> 01:27:39.080 line:80%
Mr. Vernet.

824
01:27:41.360 --> 01:27:42.720 line:80%
We are taking you into custody.

825
01:27:42.800 --> 01:27:45.680 line:80%
Criminal charges have been filed
against you for sexual assault,

826
01:27:45.760 --> 01:27:49.720 line:80%
serious bodily harm, coercion,
